name: SyncMix
description:
Hi everyone, Thank you for downloading this model would be very happy if you guys rate this model also and fill the page with images created from this model.
I have a ko-fi page where you can support me or buy me a coffee <3, it will be very much appreciated:
https://ko-fi.com/aiaricreator

V1.2

Added VAE vae-ft-mse-840000-ema-prune

Has better face details

Please use Adetailer for better face details : https://github.com/Bing-su/adetailer

V1

Remember to use VAE. I use vae-ft-mse-840000-ema-prune


Recommended Parameters:

Sampler: DPM++ 2M Karras or DPM++ SDE Karras

Steps: 20~40

Hires upscaler: 4x-UltraSharp or R-ESRGAN 4x+

Hires upscale: 2

Hires steps: 15

Denoising strength: 0.2~0.5

clip skip 2


Enjoy and if you like please give credit to me where you are posting the images
